Wrappers need compiling. See unistring/INSTALL or simply:
make

To run:
./main.lua

Dependencies:
GNOME bindings:
	http://lua-gtk.luaforge.net/
PCRE bindings:
	http://lrexlib.luaforge.net/
LuaSQL with SQLite3 backend:
	http://www.luaforge.net/projects/luasql
Unicode string C library:
	http://www.gnu.org/software/libunistring/
XdgUtils:
	http://portland.freedesktop.org/
GNU Wget:
	http://www.gnu.org/software/wget/

To satisfy all dependencies on Debian:
aptitude install liblua5.1-gnome-0
aptitude install liblua5.1-rex-pcre0
aptitude install liblua5.1-sql-sqlite3-dev
aptitude install libunistring-dev
aptitude install wget

Optional dependencies:

-- to grab web-pages:
CutyCapt:
	http://cutycapt.sourceforge.net/
	(aptitude install cutycapt)

-- to modify thumbs:
ImageMagick's convert:
	http://www.imagemagick.org/script/convert.php
	(aptitude install imagemagick)

